        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7170",
        "content": "he Of the Hundred Tales of love-where did they lay Their bones, distinguished from our common clay In death as life?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
