        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7170",
        "content": "Once did She hold the gorgeous East in fee And was the safeguard of the West; the worth Of Venice did not fall below her birth, Venice, the eldest child of liberty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
