        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7170",
        "content": "When her long life hath reach'd its final day: Men are we, and must grieve when even the shade Of that which once was great has pass'd away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
