        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7170",
        "content": "Not a drum was heard, not a funeral note, As his corpse to the rampart we hurried; Not a soldier discharged his farewell shot O'er the grave where our hero we buried.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
